headline: Intercontinental Exchange (ICE): Evaluating Valuation After Recent Cool-Off in Share Momentum
summary: Intercontinental Exchange (ICE) is making the rounds this week, but not because of a headline-grabbing corporate event. Sometimes, stocks grab our attention simply by how they trade. Recent price shifts might be prompting investors to step back and ask whether there is something more beneath the surface, or if the market is just taking a breather after a solid run. ICE shares have recorded a muted move over the past month, trailing off just under 6%, with momentum cooling after posting a 12%...
